General review: Mama Joza is a restaurant located in Kuwait, serving a selection of Pastries & Sweets, Desserts, Egyptian that delivers across Abdullah Al-Mubarak - West Jeleeb, Abdullah Al-Salem, Abu Ftaira, Abu Halifa and Abu Hasaniya.; Their best selling dishes are Cheesy Luqaimat, Mix Sweets Large, Mars Chocolate and Boksha Chocolate, although they have a variety of dishes and meals to choose from like Pastries & Sweets, Desserts, Egyptian.; They have been reviewed 682 times by talabat users, with a rating of 4.5.
